3	## What This Is
4	
5	Evident is a constraint programming language where programs are collections of
6	constraints over sets, and a Z3 SMT solver finds satisfying assignments.  The
7	central abstraction is `schema`: a named set defined by membership conditions.
8	Querying a schema asks whether a satisfying assignment exists.
